data.description: NEW ROOF INSTALLED 12/19/2020,  NEW A/C REPLACED 2019. Refrigerator, Washer and dryer included! Bring your offers! Motivated Seller. Welcome to 5710 Berkshire Ridge Dr. Sugar Land, TX. located in very well established Riverpark, at walking distance to community pool, park and playground! Easy access to Grand Parkway 99 and US 59! This "one of a kind" 4 Bedroom one story home features a wonderful split floor plan with a large and open concept living room area with wood floor. Spacious breakfast area and kitchen with lots of cabinets. Formal Dining room with wood floor, could easily be converted to a study/office/game room depending on your needs. Master Bedroom in rear of home updated with gorgeous wood floor, has direct access to backyard and hot tub. Ensuite Master bedroom with double sinks includes separate whirlpool tub and shower and his and hers closet plus a specious vanity area. Other 3 Bedroom and second bathroom are located in separate hall from master for extra privacy.
